ent-RMCBeltHolsterNailgun = customized nailgun holster
    .desc = Combination of a M276 pistol holster and engineering toolbelt that have been cannibalized into a unique belt that can holster a compact nailgun and two spare nailgun magazines.
ent-RMCM300SOCOMBelt = пояс для боеприпасов .458 SOCOM M300
    .desc = Пояс, предназначенный для хранения крупнокалиберных патронов .458 SOCOM для тяжёлой винтовки XM88.
ent-RMCM82FHolster = M276 pattern M82F flare gun holster rig
    .desc = he M276 is the standard load-bearing equipment of the UNMC. It consists of a modular belt with various clips. This version is for the M82F flare gun and can additionally store up to 16 flares.
